quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  19,1,"Kaf, Ha, Ya, Ayn, Swad."
  19,2,"Obwitsulisio bwetsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khumusumba wuwe Zakaria."
  19,3,"Olwa yalanga Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi omulango kwobwifisi."
  19,4,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, toto ebikumba bianje bimalile okhuba ebiteshele, ne omurwe kwanje kwakhanga tsimbutsi, ne shindali weyikhabi imbi tawe Nyasaye wanje Omulesi khulwa okhukhusaba."
  19,5,"Ne toto esie eyendelanga Abandu banje nindakharulaho, ne omukhasi wanje nomukumba. Kho mbelesia witsa okhutong’a mushilenje shianje okhurula khwiwe."
  19,6,"Witsa okhuchelama esie nende okhuchelama olwibulo lwa Yaqub, ne Nyasaye wanje omulesi omukhole omwene abe uchamisia.”"
  19,7,"Ewe Zakaria, toto efwe khukhwetsanga amakhuwa akomwikhoyo ko (okhwibula) omwana, elira lilie ni Yahya, khushili okhuhelesiakhwo yesiyesi imbeli wuwe elira shinga lino."
  19,8,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ndakhanyoola endie omwana omukhasi wanje nali omukumba, nasi ndamala okhukofula muno?”"
  19,9,"Naboola mbu: “Ne endio nilwa kali. Nyasaye wuwo omulesi aboolele mbu: 'Kano ni amangu muno khwisie, ne toto ndakhuloonga khale, ne shiwali eshindu tawe.'""
  19,10,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje omulesi kholela eshimanyisio.” Naboola mbu: “Eshimanyisio shishio ni mbu sholanyala okhuboola nende abandu khutsinyanga tsitaru tawe nawe nolisa omulamu habwene.”"
  19,11,"Mana narulila abandu baye okhurula mu mihirab, nabasomeselia nomukhono mbu: “Tswenule Nyasaye itsuli nende ingoloobe.”"